        <description>&lt;h2&gt;Pontifications&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MSDN blog post from 2016:&lt;a href=&quot;https://blogs.msdn.microsoft.com/commandline/2016/11/17/do-not-change-linux-files-using-windows-apps-and-tools/&quot;&gt;DO NOT, under ANY circumstances, create and/or modify Linux files using Windows apps, tools, scripts, consoles, etc.&lt;/a&gt;:

&lt;ul&gt;
