      <item>
        <title>How to setup github credential caching on Windows Linux subsystem</title>
        <description>&lt;h2&gt;Pontifications&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Just one command from &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/45925964/how-to-use-git-credential-store-on-wsl-ubuntu-on-windows&quot;&gt;How to use Git credential store on WSL (Ubuntu on Windows)?&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;git config &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;--global&lt;/span&gt; credential.helper cache
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;I didn&amp;#39;t have to change the timeout in ~/.gitconfig but just in case here&amp;#39;s the line to add&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-&quot; data-lang=&quot;&quot;&gt;[credential]
        helper = cache --timeout=144000
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
        <pubDate>Fri, 02 Mar 2018 00:00:00 -0800</pubDate>
        <link>http://rolandtanglao.com/2018/03/02/p2-how-to-setup-github-credential-caching/</link>
        <guid isPermaLink="true">http://rolandtanglao.com/2018/03/02/p2-how-to-setup-github-credential-caching/</guid>
        
        
      </item>
    
